Interface Summary
WordCounterInterface The Interface that defines the methods of the WordCounter class.
 

Class Summary
FileResults The Results class holds the Filename and Word count Map for a given File.
LabMainWindow This is the main window of operation for the entire program.
ThreadControl This class creates WordCounter objects to process text files and count words This class will create an ArrayList of WordCounters and an Array of Threads to run each of them.
TotalResults This class holds Total word and count in a map.
WordCounter Iterates through a text file to find unique words along w/ count.
